title: Arbor Snowboards :: The Superpark Video
description:
Brandon Hammid, Sammy Spiteri, Erik Leon, Joe Bosler, Pat Reddy, Scotty Vine, Nick Visconti and Curtis Woodman come together at Snowboarder Magazine's Superpark 16 for some good times shredding. This is the offical Battle of the Brands edit that made it to the final round.
